### Zentto Web3 — ejemplos de uso (VS Code REST Client / IntelliJ HTTP)
@base = http://localhost:4100/api

### Health
GET {{base}}/health

### Crear wallet del minero
POST {{base}}/wallets

### Crear wallet de usuario
POST {{base}}/wallets

### Encolar minado (sustituir MINER_ADDRESS)
POST {{base}}/mining
Content-Type: application/json

{ "minerAddress": "MINER_ADDRESS" }

### Estado del job de minado (sustituir JOB_ID)
GET {{base}}/mining/jobs/JOB_ID

### Saldo del minero
GET {{base}}/wallets/MINER_ADDRESS/balance

### Firmar una transacción (helper de demo — sustituir PRIVATE_KEY / TO_ADDRESS)
POST {{base}}/wallets/sign
Content-Type: application/json

{ "privateKey": "PRIVATE_KEY", "toAddress": "TO_ADDRESS", "amount": 10, "fee": 1 }

### Enviar la transacción firmada (pegar el payload devuelto por /wallets/sign)
POST {{base}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAddress": "FROM",
  "toAddress": "TO",
  "amount": 10,
  "fee": 1,
  "timestamp": 0,
  "signature": "SIGNATURE"
}

### Mempool
GET {{base}}/transactions/pending

### Cadena completa
GET {{base}}/chain

### Validar la cadena
GET {{base}}/chain/validate

### Screening AML
GET {{base}}/compliance/screen/MINER_ADDRESS

### Informe de cumplimiento (scoring + IA)
POST {{base}}/compliance/report
Content-Type: application/json

{ "address": "MINER_ADDRESS" }

### Grafo de transferencias
GET {{base}}/analytics/graph

### Hubs tipo exchange
GET {{base}}/analytics/hubs?minDegree=5

### Relaciones de una address
GET {{base}}/analytics/address/MINER_ADDRESS/relations

### Trazar ruta de fondos
GET {{base}}/analytics/trace?from=A&to=B
